Matlab functions in the dir src are from $FREESURFER_HOME/matlab to be compiled 
for use with Matlab Compiled Runtime.

Some minor typographical edits have been made to allow compilation under R2023a.

Functions needed for mris_compute_lgi have been edited to accommodate numerical
arguments passed in as strings via the run_matlab_entrypoint.sh command.

Source build stamp: freesurfer-linux-rocky8_x86_64-8.0.0-20250203-0f2bd3a

License info: https://github.com/freesurfer/freesurfer/blob/v8.0.0/LICENSE.txt

